Step-by-Step Guide
1
Start Metasploit with: msfconsole
2
Search for exploits: search type:exploit <keyword>
3
Select an exploit: use <exploit_path>
4
View options: show options
5
Set target: set RHOSTS <target_ip>
6
Set payload if needed: set PAYLOAD <payload_path>
7
Run the exploit: exploit or run
8
If successful, interact with the session
Understanding the Output
Metasploit uses color-coded output: green [+] for success, blue [*] for info, yellow [-] for failures, red [!] for errors. When an exploit works, you'll see "Meterpreter session opened" or similar.

